dict.acceptation: 关闭着的，封闭着的；密闭着的，保密的；<美>准备好了的，定了契约的；

sent.orig: At first, I opened and closed its Session object for each DAO method.
sent.trans: 一开始我在每个DAO的方法中opened和closed他们的Session对象。

sent.orig: Through the simulation experiments, it checks the validity of the closed-loop subspace model identification.
sent.trans: 通过仿真实验，验证了闭环子空间模型辨识(closed-loopSMI)算法的有效性。

sent.orig: An isolated system is obviously a closed system, but not every closed system is isolated.
sent.trans: 显然，一个隔离体系就是一个封闭体系，但并非每个封闭体系都是隔离的。

sent.orig: Are you closed to the general public, or are you just closed to everybody?
sent.trans: 你们关门不让大众进来还是不让所有的人进来？

sent.orig: I closed on my finger and made it bleed when I closed the window.
sent.trans: 我关窗子时挤破了手指。
